summary: Despite the recent pullback in crypto, BlackRock's digital ETFs are leading the industry as more retail and investment managers add crypto to their portfolios.

headline: Is There Still Opportunity in BlackRock After Another Year of Double Digit Gains?
summary: Thinking about what to do with BlackRock stock lately? If you've found yourself wondering whether you missed the boat or if there's still opportunity left, you're not alone. With shares closing recently at $1,161.16, and up a solid 14.1% so far this year, BlackRock has been hard to ignore. In just the past week, the stock notched a 2.5% gain, a nice follow-up to its mild 2.6% climb over the last month.
